<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy |  <%= name %> Hosting Servers</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; }
    }
    .animate-float { animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .animate-pulse-slow { animation: pulse 4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite; }
    .gradient-text {
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
    }
    .section-transition {
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .section-transition:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-200 font-['Inter']">
  <!-- Animated Background Elements -->
  <div class="fixed inset-0 overflow-hidden -z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 blur-xl animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-20 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 blur-xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/4 w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 blur-xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="gradient-text font-['Montserrat']"> <%= name %></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-pulse-slow">
        Premium Bot Server Hosting
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-20">
    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-700/50 mb-12 transform transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
      <div class="p-8 sm:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 gradient-text">Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
          Last Updated: <span class="text-blue-400">June 1, 2025</span>
        </p>

        <!-- Policy Sections -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <section class="section-transition bg-gray-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700/30">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
              </svg>
              Information We Collect
            </h3>
            <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-3">
              <p>When you use our Bot hosting services, we may collect:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                <li>Account information (username, email, payment details)</li>
                <li>Server usage data and performance metrics</li>
                <li>IP addresses for security and authentication</li>
                <li>Support ticket communications</li>
                <li>Website usage analytics via cookies</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="section-transition bg-gray-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700/30">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
              How We Use Your Information
            </h3>
            <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-3">
              <p>Your data helps us provide and improve our services:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                <li>To deliver and maintain your Minecraft servers</li>
                <li>For billing and account management</li>
                <li>To troubleshoot technical issues</li>
                <li>To enhance security and prevent abuse</li>
                <li>To communicate service updates and offers</li>
                <li>For legal compliance and fraud prevention</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="section-transition bg-gray-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700/30">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z" />
              </svg>
              Data Protection
            </h3>
            <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-3">
              <p>We implement industry-standard measures to protect your data:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                <li>Encryption of sensitive data in transit and at rest</li>
